text:
wooyoung merasa sedikit kesusahan ketika berjalan keluar dari lift yang sudah berhenti di lantai bawah. ramai, banyak sekali mahasiswa mengerumuni tata usaha yang memang letaknya di dekat pintu masuk gedung fakultas.
beruntung, orang-orang di sana segera menyingkir dan beberapa membantunya hingga wooyoung dapat keluar dari kerumunan dan lekas melesat menuju klinik kampus yang berada tepat di samping gedung fakultasnya.
“anak fikes masih libur, gue panggil penjaga klinik dulu aja, ya.”
yunho mengangguki ucapan chaeyeon sementara wooyoung mulai membaringkan tubuh chaewon di atas salah satu kasur di sana.
wooyoung menghela napas, lantas segera berjalan menuju kasur kosong dan mendudukkan diri di sana.
“woo, lo gak papa gendong chaewon sendirian tadi?” tanya yunho.
“gak, gue capek,” balasnya.
trans:
Wooyoung found it a bit challenging to step out of the lift as it stopped on the ground floor. The area was bustling with students gathered around the administration office, located near the entrance of the faculty building.
Fortunately, several people quickly moved aside and offered their help, allowing Wooyoung to break free from the crowd and hurry towards the campus clinic right next door.
“The FIKES students are still on break, so I'll just call the clinic staff,” Yunho said.
Chaeyeon nodded in agreement while Wooyoung gently laid Chaewon down on one of the beds in the clinic.
Sighing, Wooyoung made his way to an empty bed and settled down.
“Hey, are you okay carrying Chaewon by yourself earlier?” Yunho asked, concern in his voice.
“I’m fine, just a little tired,” Wooyoung replied.
